title: #124: Rape & Eggs (@Kathleen_McGee)
itunes:title: Rape & Eggs with Kathleen McGee
description: Kathleen McGee invited me over to the apartment she was staying in while we were in Winnipeg together and we talked about her rape. It's about as lighthearted a conversation as possible considering the subject matter. This is kind of what this podcast is all about. Stark, realistic views of the world told in funny ways. Enjoy.
